<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Document</title>

    <style>
      @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Prompt:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&display=swap");
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      a {
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      table,
      td,
      th {
        border: 1px solid black;
      }
      table {
        width: 30%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 0 auto;
        margin-top: 50px;
      }
      tr th {
        padding: 5px 20px;
      }
      tr td {
        padding-top: 4px;
        padding-bottom: 4px;
      }
      h1 {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 160px;
      }
      p {
        text-align: center;
        color: #9a9a9a;
        margin-top: 10px;
        font-style: italic;
      }
      .book {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 30px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 16px;
        padding: 6px 15px;
        font-weight: bold;
        background-color: #8bd9b3;
        color: #ffffff;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
      }
      .button-style {
        text-align: center;
      }
      .logo-img {
        width: 80px;
        height: 90px;
      }
      .logout {
        font-family: "Prompt", sans-serif;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #8bd9b3;
        margin-left: 10px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }

      .go-insert {
        background-color: #8bd9b3;
        font-family: "Prompt", sans-serif;
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 800;
        border: none;
        padding: 3px 15px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        color: white;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      }

      .button-style {
        margin-top: 30px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <a href="/logout" class="logout">LOGOUT</a>
    <h1>도서 목록</h1>
    <p>현재 도서관에 있는 도서를 확인하고 삭제할 수 있습니다.</p>
    <table>
      <tr>
        <th>도서 이름</th>
        <th>작가</th>
        <th>출판사</th>
        <th>가격</th>
      </tr>
      <% bookList.forEach(function (value) { %>
      <tr>
        <td><%=value.name %></td>
        <td><%=value.author %></td>
        <td><%=value.publisher %></td>
        <td><%=value.price %></td>
        <td><a href="/bookDelete/<%= value.id %>">삭제</a></td>
      </tr>
      <% }); %>
    </table>

    <div class="button-style">
      <button type="button" class="go-insert" onclick="location.href='/login'">
        도서신청
      </button>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
